### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/sales/api
@adminToken = TU_TOKEN_ADMIN
@editorToken = TU_TOKEN_EDITOR
@customerToken = TU_TOKEN_CUSTOMER

### ==========================================
### PHOTO — UPLOAD (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Upload photo (admin — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/photo/upload HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pro_variant_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------FormBoundary--

### ==========================================

### Upload photo (editor — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/photo/upload HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pro_variant_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------FormBoundary--

### ==========================================

### Upload photo (customer — 403 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/photo/upload HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pro_variant_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------FormBoundary--

### ==========================================

### Upload photo (sin token — 401 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/photo/upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pro_variant_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------FormBoundary--

### ==========================================

### Upload photo (variant no existe — 400 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/photo/upload HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pro_variant_id"

999
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------FormBoundary--

### ==========================================

### Upload photo (sin archivo — 400 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/photo/upload HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pro_variant_id": "1"
}

### ==========================================

### Upload photo (tipo inválido — 400 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/photo/upload HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pro_variant_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="test.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test.pdf
------FormBoundary--